         <div type="writingSession" n="1"><opener><dateline rend="right"><pb facs="MS-SCHNITZLER-B-0008-B-00002-000-00252"/><date>17. VII. 27</date>.</dateline></opener><p><salute>Lieber Arthur!</salute> Wir kommen gerne. Um <time>8</time> Uhr. D<hi rend="superscript">r</hi><space unit="chars" quantity="1"/><rs ref="#pmb3119" type="person">M</rs>. ist schon in <rs type="place" ref="#pmb521">Gastein</rs>.</p><closer>Herzlichst<lb/>Ihr<lb/><signed>Richard</signed></closer></div>
      </body>
